        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 13–14. Metaphalangium martensi sp. n., paratype, SIZK K-1254, from Rovno amber (Klesov, Pugach quarry, Ukraine), late Eocene. 13 Lateral overview of the complete animal (white arrow points the pedipalps). 14 Detail of pedipalps, lateral. Scale bars: 13: 1 mm; 14: 0.5 mm." ;
